---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About">
  <main class="sarva-main">
    <p class="sarva-section-label">About</p>
    <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:2rem">Who's behind SARVA?</h1>
    <div class="about-section">
      <p>SARVA is a one-person passion project blending two obsessions: the numbers behind modern cricket and the what-ifs of history.</p>
      <p>Started in 8th grade for friends and family, it's grown into something more serious — a place for writing that's equal parts rigorous and readable. No jargon walls, no generic scorecards. Just clear thinking on cricket and history.</p>
      <p>Every IPL 2024 match was covered. Every What If essay is written from scratch. This is what it looks like when you care about the craft.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:2rem">
        <strong style="color:var(--sarva-text)">Sarvajith Aravind Venugopal</strong><br/>
        <span>Science student · Musician · Martial artist · Blogger</span><br/>
        <a href="mailto:sarvajith.aravind@gmail.com" style="color:#4a9eff">sarvajith.aravind@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
